      "span_text": "The manifestation of the Daf-constitutive phenotype in daf-2(-) ts mutants requires DAF-16 activity; daf-2(-) ts ; daf-16(-) double-mutant animals grow as reproductive adults even at 25°C. daf-16a isoform is known to promote dauer development but has no effect on lifespan  .",
